# CGRphylo2 0.99.0

## New Features

* Initial Bioconductor submission
* Implemented core CGR (Chaos Game Representation) algorithm
* Added cgat() function for frequency matrix calculation
* Added cgrplot() function for CGR visualization
* Implemented multiple distance metrics (Euclidean, Manhattan, Squared Euclidean)
* Added parallelCGR() for efficient parallel processing
* Export functions for MEGA and PHYLIP formats
* Comprehensive vignette with examples
* Full test suite with testthat

## Functions

* `cgat()` - Calculate CGR frequency matrices
* `cgrplot()` - Generate CGR plot coordinates
* `matrixDistance()` - Calculate pairwise distances
* `calculateDistanceMatrix()` - Compute full distance matrix
* `fastafile_new()` - Filter sequences by N content
* `create_meta()` - Extract sequence metadata
* `saveMegaDistance()` - Export to MEGA format
* `savePhylipDistance()` - Export to PHYLIP format
* `parallelCGR()` - Parallel frequency matrix calculation

## Documentation

* Comprehensive package vignette
* Detailed function documentation with examples
* README with quick start guide
* Citation information

